        "cooked": "<p>Since this would require designing a new UI for desktop (unfortunately it’s not quite as easy as just copying the implementation for mobile) and also a transition between the two when the window reaches a certain size, it would be quite a bit of work to do this. Most people use Signal in landscape mode on desktop, so I don’t think the devs will spend the time on this.</p>",
