        "cooked": "<p>I mentioned mobile ui because they won’t have to think of a new design. Yes, they would have to rethink the code, but they already have a working and community-accepted design, so they can write the code for that only and I disagree that most people use it in portrait mode because I have seen many people use it. Not only signal  but most social media is more practical in portrait mode. Well, no problem, I am switching back to Telegram.</p>",
